## Statement
```
Given a list of distinct numbers, swap the minimum and the maximum and print the resulting list.
```
## Sample Input
```
3 4 5 2 1
```
## Sample Output
```
3 4 1 2 5
```
## Code
```
numbers_in_list = [int(i) for i in input().split()]
minimum = numbers_in_list.index(min(numbers_in_list))
maximum = numbers_in_list.index(max(numbers_in_list))
numbers_in_list[minimum],numbers_in_list[maximum] = numbers_in_list[maximum],numbers_in_list[minimum]
print(numbers_in_list)
```
